snippet.title: Metaverser Skate Park | Cool Gameplay by Luuca
snippet.description:
In Metaverser besides having an income, you can also have fun day and night and enjoy being.
 
Luca, one of the talented Metaverser players, created a video while he was playing in Metaverser’s interesting Skate Park on one beautiful night of Metaverser under the moonlight.

We suggest you start playing for free now, have fun, and earn money.

We are awarding Luca a Happy Walk NFT because of his amazing game and for spreading this good vibe. 

We hope for you, Luca, to be always happy. 😃

https://metaverser.me
Video by : https://www.instagram.com/luuca.mm

#MTVT #metaverse #playtoearn #freetoplay
